cast.overview: Valentin is Acapulco's resident playboy, until a former fling leaves a baby on his doorstep and him heading with her out of Mexico.
cast.title: Instructions Not Included

details.biography: Melissa Temme is an East Coast-based actress who can be seen most recently in films such as Pantelion's "Instructions Not Included," Opening Act's, "The Rise of the Fellowship," the web series, "The ABC's of Online Dating," and the short-film, "As Is," runner-up for Best Film at DC's 48 Hr Film Project and winner of Best Ensemble Cast. She has appeared in commercials for the likes of Baby Jogger, Navy Mutual and PetSmart and she hosts Audi of America's monthly internal news show, Audi Progress. Melissa has a degree in psychology from Indiana University and is married to saxophonist, Steve Temme. Together they have two little girls who keep life sweet (and hilarious).  - IMDb Mini Biography By: Melissa Temme
details.name: Melissa Temme
